(13601, 'Faroviga 100mg 12 f.c.tab.', 'فاروفيجا 100مجم 12 قرص', '70.5', '108', 'Sildenafil', 'Pharopharma', 'Tab', 'أقراص', '', 'Tonic for men', '100mg', 'Sildenafil is a phosphodiesterase-5 (PDE5) inhibitor that is predominantly employed for two primary indications:
